			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;2. Set the debug option in the Debug Book to &quot;make a deal with Raphael&quot;&#xD;&#xA;3. Free Hope with Orphic Hammer&#xD;&#xA;4. teleport S_LOW_HouseOfHope_CheckMainTreasuresTrigger" />
